text: Yara Kakish (born 21 August 1991) is a Jordanian female ju-jitsu practitioner. Her husband Basel Fanous is also a ju-jitsu practitioner and has represented Jordan in international competitive events. She represented Jordan at the 2018 Asian Games and claimed a bronze medal in the women's 62kg ne-waza event. == References == Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Jordanian female martial artists Category:Ju-jitsu practitioners at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for Jordan Category:Sportspeople from Amman Category:Asian Games medalists in ju-jitsu
